TY  - JOUR
T1  - Testing at the Source: Analytics-Enabled Risk-Based Sampling of Food Supply Chains in China
AU  - Jin, Cangyu
AU  - Levi, Retsef
AU  - Liang, Qiao
AU  - Renegar, Nicholas
AU  - Springs, Stacy
AU  - Zhou, Jiehong
AU  - Zhou, Weihua
Y1  - 2021/01/22
